       versions interprétées, exigeant la présence de Python3, tkinter, tkinter.checkbutton, os, sys, time, subprocess, scrolledtext, threading.timer
1 - edit efibootmgr_Us.bash and replace "/home/----path to-----" by the path to the efibootmgr_Us.py program
2 - créate on your desktop a launcher pointing to efibootmgr_Us.bash with "terminal=true" (mandatory) and icon=efibootmgr_nvram.png
3 - That's all

